{"tid":1311843,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"同朋友去旅行真係麻撚煩","createTime":"2019-07-13T11:05:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T05:43:17.000Z","uid":47983,"like":88,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"a7d4e402aed99a0286a850a63743f1f45024b8e1","tid":1311843,"uid":47983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T11:05:37.000Z","msg":"話說啱啱同朋友去旅行<br />\n全程閪到不得了<br />\n已經醒水 之後同佢分開行㗎啦<br />\n就算返香港嗰時 去機場都係各自自去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我早到 早啲排隊上機放行李<br />\n當我差唔多上機時 後邊仲有勁多人<br />\n佢嗰刻先至到 扮晒可憐咁同我講「可唔可以打尖」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢真係當後邊啲人透明㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就話「唔好啦，後邊咁多人」<br />\n<br />\n轉頭上到機 就閪晒面 好似殺佢全家咁嘅樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最搞笑佢自己憎人打尖 但自己又想打人尖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌 同朋友去旅行真係麻撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4878859258917c2351fff047fd96d633cad6e219","tid":1311843,"uid":83853,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T11:08:52.000Z","msg":"陪佢一齊排最後<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"028ed11e7cb652a6d4215d145af1d99ab695cc51","tid":1311843,"uid":206370,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T11:09:34.000Z","msg":"你肯定你哋fd到可以一齊去旅行？定湊腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"968bf9156b31b934362bdeedf384200a298a185b","tid":1311843,"uid":274246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T11:10:36.000Z","msg":"上機都要打尖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcfa9bf401274d98372a36bca65d5921aa345e06","tid":1311843,"uid":47983,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"4878859258917c2351fff047fd96d633cad6e219","tid":1311843,"uid":83853,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"cited